"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1929240-tom-daley-olympics-2024-gold-medal-team-gb\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley and diving partner Noah Williams bagged a silver medal in the men's synchronised 10m diving at the2024 Olympics,missing out on gold to Chinese duo Junjie Lian and Hao Yang.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.377919263616267e-43, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9987971299798071, \"rank\": 0.0005718532486654541, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"score\": 0.9888847157819461, \"rank\": 0.009316001362736475, \"text\": \"Lian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 50, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's synchronised 10m\", \"from\": 68, \"to\": 94}, {\"ngram\": \"the2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 141}, {\"ngram\": \"Hao Yang\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Already an Olympic champion and bonafide legend of the sport, Daley served up a valiant effort alongside Williams to secureTeam GB'sfifth medal of the Games.\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"a valiant effort\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"GB'sfifth medal\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also Daley's fifth overall Olympic medal and his first second-place finish at the Games, having previously picked up three bronze medals and one gold.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley's fifth overall Olympic medal\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"his first second-place finish\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"three bronze medals\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"one gold\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after he picked up his silver medal, Daley told theBBC: \\\"It's just so special, this time deciding to come back, not knowing if I'd make the synchro team, let alone qualify for the Olympics, now to be here in Paris, diving in front of my son, who is right there, who actually asked me to come back, it's so special.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999977975761947, \"rank\": 2.2024287591950926e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his silver medal\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"theBBC\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"the synchro team\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 699}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"my son\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your ultimate guide\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clickhereto buy\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it completes the set, I now have one of every colour.\\\"\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the set\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"every colour\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Williams, it's his first Olympic medal, having made his Games debut three years ago in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9966714057954275, \"rank\": 0.003335911043820381, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"his first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"his Games\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Williams said: \\\"From third last to second, my coach passed after Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9966714057954275, \"rank\": 0.003335911043820381, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"second\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not talk too much or I will cry.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But no I am happy... \\\"I have come a long way in the last year, just practising, I am really glad it paid off here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When quizzed on how his return to diving went, Daley later added: \\\"Once you are an athlete, you know what you need to do, you have to train smarter.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how his return\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to prioritise things in your life as well as in the pool.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A happy athlete is an athlete who dives well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A happy athlete\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attention turned to Daley's future, with the 30-year-old quizzed on whether he'd consider competing at the Los Angeles Games in four years times.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Attention\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley's future\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"the Los Angeles Games\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"four years times\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He responded: \\\"I do not know.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For right now, I want to enjoy today, so we will see what the future holds.\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But right now, I just want to go and squish my little one.\\\"\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley and Williams posted impressive numbers throughout the meet but were unable to keep pace with the world champions China, who were by far and away the best duo on the diving board.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6236512863182223, \"rank\": 0.5954801871211137, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"impressive numbers\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"the meet\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"pace\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the world champions\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"far and away the best duo\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"the diving board\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley and Williams finished up with a score of 463.44, while winners Lian and Yang topped the podium with 490.35 points.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2193, \"end\": 2197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"score\": 0.9888847157819461, \"rank\": 0.009316001362736475, \"text\": \"Lian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lian_the_Great\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"winners\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"Yang\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"490.35 points\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley's trainer Jane Figueiredo told theBBCafter the event: \\\"I am just over the moon for both of them, there is been a lot going on.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Beale\", \"score\": 0.9999959893578698, \"rank\": 2.76051729645576e-06, \"text\": \"Jane\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Beale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Beale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theBBCafter\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"the moon\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngr